---
    import performanceImage from "/performance.png"
    import integrationImage from "/integration.png"
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-w-7xl mx-auto gap-6 pt-14 pb-32">
    <div class="p-16 bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold">Webflow developer at the intersection of design and code.</div>
        <div class=" mt-5">I turn your designs into pixel-perfect Webflow sites with great attention to detail and elegant animations. Say goodbye to the stressful back and forth with developers who have no feel for design. Additionally, I offer consulting services during your design phase with my experience in UI/UX and animation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
            <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text from-cyan-500 bg-gradient-to-r to-green-500 flex">50<span class="text-3xl">+</span></div>
            <div class="">Happy clients</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
            <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text from-cyan-400 bg-gradient-to-r to-blue-500">6<span class="text-2xl"> Years</span></div>
            <div class="">Experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
            <div class=" text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text from-indigo-500 bg-gradient-to-r to-purple-400 flex">80<div class="text-3xl">+</div></div>
            <div class="">Webflow projects</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
            <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text from-yellow-400 bg-gradient-to-r to-pink-600">100<span class="text-2xl font-semibold">%</span></div>
            <div class="">Passion</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold p-10">Lightning-fast load time.</div>
        <div class="mb-8"><img class="w-[90%]" src={performanceImage} alt="Performance Image"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[rgb(28,29,30)] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="mb-8"><img class="" src={integrationImage} alt="Performance Image"></div>
        <div class="text-3xl text-center font-semibold p-4">Custom <br/> Integrations.</div>
    </div>
</div>
